OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FThomas stabbed his friend 37 times `
OL,7,Fincluding to the neck, chest, head and
OL,8,Fback ` and people on the street
OL,9,Fdescribed screams of "horror" from
OL,10,Finside the house.
OL,12,FThe court heard that Thomas had
OL,13,Fsearched online for the anatomy of the
OL,14,Fneck before going back to the house.
OL,16,FThomas was sentenced to life
OL,17,Fimprisonment on Friday, 24 January at
OL,18,FCardiff Crown Court and ordered to
OL,19,Fserve a minimum of 19 years.
