OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, Mr
OL,7,FBush's sister Catrin spoke on behalf
OL,8,Fof herself and her brother Alex `
OL,9,Fdescribing her brother's death as a
OL,10,F"barbaric crime".
OL,12,F"I cannot put into words how traumatic
OL,13,Fand awful this experience was, and I
OL,14,Fstill have intense moments of panic
OL,15,Fwhen I think about this," she said.
OL,17,F"Myself and Alex cannot begin to
OL,18,Fcomprehend the fear and suffering that
OL,19,FWill endured on that day. We are truly
OL,20,Fhaunted from the horror of it and this
OL,21,Fwill live with us forever."
