OL,6,FDuring the trial, the jury heard from
OL,7,FDr Panchu Xavier, a consultant
OL,8,Fforensic psychiatrist at Ashworth, who
OL,9,Fsaid the defendant could have been
OL,10,Fhaving a psychotic episode during the
OL,11,Fattack and for "up to six months
OL,12,Fbefore the event".
OL,14,FThe jury also heard Thomas had been
OL,15,Farrested for breaking into Buckingham
OL,16,FPalace a few months before the attack
OL,17,Fon Mr Bush.
