OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FThomas told officers he was looking
OL,7,Ffor "energy fields" between the Palace
OL,8,Fand Cleopatra's Needle, an obelisk in
OL,9,Fcentral London.
OL,11,FHe was rugby-tackled by an officer
OL,12,Fafter he told them he was "over now so
OL,13,Fyou may as well show me round".
OL,15,FWilliam Bush's father, John, told
OL,16,FCardiff Crown Court the lives of his
OL,17,Ffamily changed overnight when his son
OL,18,Fdied and the effects would stay with
OL,19,Fthem forever.
