OL,6,FHe said in a victim impact statement:
OL,7,F"This is not normal grief, where death
OL,8,Fis part of human existence and loss
OL,9,Fcan be accepted and memories of loved
OL,10,Fones celebrated. We are not there yet,
OL,11,Fand there is not yet any closure for
OL,12,Fus.
OL,14,F"We carry on with our own lives, but
OL,15,Fwe know we are always pretending. We
OL,16,Fhave also had to watch the pain of the
OL,17,Floss for Will's brother Alex and
OL,18,Fsister Catrin, and their partners, Ed
OL,19,Fand Olivia, and Will's girlfriend Ella.
