OL,6,F"We will share their future happiness,
OL,7,Fbut we will always be tinged with
OL,8,Fsadness and loss. We continue with our
OL,9,Flives because we must, but time cannot
OL,10,Ffully heal the loss of Will's.
OL,12,F"Imagine all the things that you would
OL,13,Fhave missed if you had died at 23 `
OL,14,Fmarriage, children, family, the daily
OL,15,Fjoys of the life. His life mattered.
OL,16,FGod bless you, Will."
