OL,6,FWilliam Bush's partner Ella Jefferies
OL,7,Ftold Cardiff Crown Court in a victim
OL,8,Fimpact statement how they were
OL,9,Fplanning their future lives together
OL,10,Fwhen he died.
OL,12,F"To lose Will has meant we have lost
OL,13,Fthe future that we have both planned
OL,14,Fand prepared for," she said.
OL,16,F"Will and I had achieved a lot in the
OL,17,Fyear that we were together.
OL,18,FUltimately, I have lost a person that
OL,19,FI love.
