OL,6,FThe judge added that no sentence could
OL,7,Fmake up for the loss of Mr Bush, and
OL,8,Fthat it was clear that his family was
OL,9,F"haunted daily" by what had happened.
OL,11,FShe sentenced Dylan Thomas to life
OL,12,Fwith a minimum term of 19 years.
OL,14,FTaking into consideration the time
OL,15,Fspent on remand, Thomas will have to
OL,16,Fserve 17 years and 337 days
OL,17,Fimprisonment before he can be
OL,18,Fconsidered for parole.
